# @param {Integer} purchase_amount
# @return {Integer}
def account_balance_after_purchase(purchase_amount)
    # Find the remainder when dividing by 10
    remainder = purchase_amount % 10

    # Calculate the rounded amount
    if remainder == 0
        rounded_amount = purchase_amount
    elsif remainder <= 5
        rounded_amount = purchase_amount - remainder + 10
    else
        rounded_amount = purchase_amount + (10 - remainder)
    end

    # Calculate the final account balance
    100 - rounded_amount
end
